Not only is it an interesting intellectual exercise (to me, at least), but it has been demonstrated time and again that rational, clear feedback on spells, abilities, and items (both current and future) can and does product change, most often for the better.<br>
<br>
Celestial Cleansing in its first incarnation was similarly underpowered, only after continued feedback (much of which was on this board) and demonstration of its low utilitiy was it changed.<br>
