<br>
CC with SCR3 = 4.04 efficiency, is ~43% more efficient than Sup heal with the aa goodies.<br>
<br>
SC with SCR3 = 3.91 efficiency, is ~4% more efficient than divine light with aa goodies.<br>
<br>
It doesn't change the substance of your post though, we are getting hosed with a less efficient spell "upgrade", I just wanted to point that out.<br>
